				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Players get a disguise in House of Hope as an attire item: while it's equipped, Eternal Debtors are not hostile towards the character. \r\n\r\nIn Boudoir there's a big chance that one character will be naked (after all the items are unequipped) after an encounter with Incubus, so we place a small warning near the exit if a character is not in disguise"
